Hardware e Perifericheil mio iPhone

L’analisi al microscopio svela i segreti di Apple A19, il SOC di iPhone 17

Di Mauro Notarianni

24 Set 2025

<img 
                                        fetchpriority="high" 
                                        width="741" 
                                        height="486" 
                                        class="entry-thumb" 
                                        src="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/09/dieA19-741x486.jpg.webp" srcset="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/09/dieA19-741x486.jpg.webp 741w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/09/dieA19-50x34.jpg.webp 50w" sizes="(max-width: 741px) 100vw, 741px" 
